---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<style>
  .donate {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #1d1d1f;
  }

  /* ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .donate-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5.5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .donate-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 55% at 50% 0%,
      rgba(0,113,227,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .donate-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #0071e3;
    background: rgba(0,113,227,0.08);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .donate-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.06;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 auto 1.1rem;
    max-width: 640px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .donate-hero p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.1rem);
    color: #6e6e73;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ── OPEN COLLECTIVE ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .donate-oc {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .donate-oc-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .donate-oc-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; text-align: center; }
    .donate-oc-inner img { margin: 0 auto; }
  }

  .donate-oc-logo {
    height: 165px;
    width: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .donate-oc-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .donate-oc-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #6e6e73;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
  }

  .donate-oc-text .recommended {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #34c759;
    background: rgba(52,199,89,0.1);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  /* ── PRIMARY BUTTON ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.6rem;
    border-radius: 980px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    background: #0071e3;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    transition: background 0.18s, transform 0.18s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: #0080f5; transform: scale(1.02); }

  /* ── ALTERNATIVES ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .donate-alt {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .donate-alt-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .donate-alt-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .donate-alt-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }

  .donate-alt-header p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #86868b;
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .donate-note {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.825rem;
    color: #6e6e73;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .donate-note a { color: #0071e3; text-decoration: none; }
  .donate-note a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .donate-platforms {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) { .donate-platforms { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .donate-platform-card {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    transition: box-shadow 0.25s, transform 0.25s;
  }

  .donate-platform-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.09);
  }

  .donate-platform-card .plabel {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #86868b;
  }

  .donate-platform-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .btn-patreon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 980px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    background: #F96854;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.18s;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .btn-patreon:hover { background: #f75740; }

  .btn-paypal {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 980px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    background: #0070BA;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.18s;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .btn-paypal:hover { background: #005ea6; }

  /* ── DONORS & GOALS ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  .donate-goals {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  .donate-goals-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .donate-goals-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .donate-goals-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .donate-goals-header p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #6e6e73;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  /* Prose body */
  .donate-prose p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #3a3a3c;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
  }

  .donate-prose strong { color: #1d1d1f; font-weight: 600; }

  .donate-prose a { color: #0071e3; text-decoration: none; }
  .donate-prose a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .donate-prose ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 1.25rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .donate-prose ul li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #3a3a3c;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    padding-left: 0.25rem;
  }

  /* Funded items */
  .donate-funded {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .donate-funded-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #3a3a3c;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .donate-funded-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .donate-funded-item::before {
    content: '';
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #34c759;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 5px;
  }

  /* Thank you badge */
  .donate-thankyou {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0071e3 0%, #0051a8 100%);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* LTS goal items */
  .donate-lts-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #3a3a3c;
  }

  .donate-lts-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .lts-badge {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .lts-funded   { background: rgba(52,199,89,0.12);  color: #1a7a35; }
  .lts-pending  { background: rgba(255,159,10,0.12); color: #8a5a00; }
  .lts-unfunded { background: rgba(255,59,48,0.10);  color: #9e1c15; }
</style>

<BaseLayout>
<div class="donate">

  <!-- ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="donate-hero">
    <span class="donate-eyebrow">
      <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M6 1.5C4 1.5 2 3 2 5c0 3 4 6.5 4 6.5s4-3.5 4-6.5c0-2-2-3.5-4-3.5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
      Support Ubuntu Budgie
    </span>
    <h1>Help us keep<br/>Budgie flying.</h1>
    <p>Every donation, large or small, helps fund development, infrastructure and the future of Ubuntu Budgie.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ── OPEN COLLECTIVE ───────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="donate-oc">
    <div class="donate-oc-inner">
      <img src="/icons/oc.svg" alt="Open Collective Logo" class="donate-oc-logo" />
      <div class="donate-oc-text">
        <h2>Donate via Open Collective</h2>
        <p>Open Collective is our preferred donation platform. It provides full financial transparency — you can see exactly how every pound is spent, from developer payments to infrastructure costs.</p>
        <a href="https://opencollective.com/ubuntubudgie/contribute" class="btn-primary">
          Donate to our Collective
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M2.5 9.5l7-7M9.5 2.5H5M9.5 2.5v4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── ALTERNATIVES ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="donate-alt">
    <div class="donate-alt-inner">
      <div class="donate-alt-header">
        <h2>Other ways to donate</h2>
        <p>Recurring donations and custom one-time donations are both available.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="donate-note">
        Paypal and Patreon are still active, but we encourage supporters to use Open Collective — it has lower commission fees, meaning maximum impact per donation.<br/>
        Special thanks to our fiscal host: <a href="https://opencollective.com/the-social-change-nest" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Social Change Nest</a>
      </div>

      <div class="donate-platforms">

        <div class="donate-platform-card">
          <span class="plabel">Recurring donation</span>
          <h3>Patreon</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#6e6e73;margin:0;line-height:1.55;">Monthly support with exclusive updates for patrons.</p>
          <a href="https://www.patreon.com/user?u=3038166&ty=h&u=3038166" class="btn-patreon">
            <svg width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M15.385 1.015c-4.418 0-8 3.582-8 8s3.582 8 8 8 8-3.582 8-8-3.582-8-8-8zM.985 23V1.015h3V23h-3z"/>
            </svg>
            Support on Patreon
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="donate-platform-card">
          <span class="plabel">One-time or monthly</span>
          <h3>PayPal</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#6e6e73;margin:0;line-height:1.55;">Flexible one-time or recurring PayPal donations.</p>
          <a href="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=ZZZLS8W5QC8US" class="btn-paypal">
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32px" height="32px" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none">
<circle cx="24" cy="24" r="20" fill="#0070BA"/>
<path d="M32.3305 18.0977C32.3082 18.24 32.2828 18.3856 32.2542 18.5351C31.2704 23.5861 27.9046 25.331 23.606 25.331H21.4173C20.8916 25.331 20.4486 25.7127 20.3667 26.2313L19.2461 33.3381L18.9288 35.3527C18.8755 35.693 19.1379 36 19.4815 36H23.3634C23.8231 36 24.2136 35.666 24.286 35.2127L24.3241 35.0154L25.055 30.3772L25.1019 30.1227C25.1735 29.6678 25.5648 29.3338 26.0245 29.3338H26.6051C30.3661 29.3338 33.3103 27.8068 34.1708 23.388C34.5303 21.5421 34.3442 20.0008 33.393 18.9168C33.1051 18.59 32.748 18.3188 32.3305 18.0977Z" fill="white" fill-opacity="0.6"/>
<path d="M31.3009 17.6871C31.1506 17.6434 30.9955 17.6036 30.8364 17.5678C30.6766 17.5328 30.5127 17.5018 30.3441 17.4748C29.754 17.3793 29.1074 17.334 28.4147 17.334H22.5676C22.4237 17.334 22.2869 17.3666 22.1644 17.4254C21.8948 17.5551 21.6944 17.8104 21.6459 18.1229L20.402 26.0013L20.3662 26.2311C20.4481 25.7126 20.8911 25.3308 21.4168 25.3308H23.6055C27.9041 25.3308 31.2699 23.5851 32.2537 18.5349C32.2831 18.3854 32.3078 18.2398 32.33 18.0975C32.0811 17.9655 31.8115 17.8525 31.5212 17.7563C31.4496 17.7324 31.3757 17.7094 31.3009 17.6871Z" fill="white" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
<path d="M21.6461 18.1231C21.6946 17.8105 21.895 17.5552 22.1646 17.4264C22.2879 17.3675 22.4239 17.3349 22.5678 17.3349H28.4149C29.1077 17.3349 29.7542 17.3803 30.3444 17.4757C30.513 17.5027 30.6768 17.5338 30.8367 17.5687C30.9957 17.6045 31.1508 17.6443 31.3011 17.688C31.3759 17.7103 31.4498 17.7334 31.5222 17.7564C31.8125 17.8527 32.0821 17.9664 32.331 18.0976C32.6237 16.231 32.3287 14.9601 31.3194 13.8093C30.2068 12.5424 28.1986 12 25.629 12H18.169C17.6441 12 17.1963 12.3817 17.1152 12.9011L14.0079 32.5969C13.9467 32.9866 14.2473 33.3381 14.6402 33.3381H19.2458L20.4022 26.0014L21.6461 18.1231Z" fill="white"/>
</svg>
            Support on PayPal
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── DONORS & GOALS ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="donate-goals">
    <div class="donate-goals-inner">

      <div class="donate-goals-header">
        <h2>Donors &amp; Goals</h2>
        <p>We support open source and any money raised goes towards open source developers as well as Ubuntu Budgie itself. Full transparency is our goal.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="donate-prose">

        <p>Patreon donations are made visible on confirmation at the beginning of the next month. PayPal donations appear as soon as possible after receipt. We invest donations to provide a better product, support our developers, and keep the lights on.</p>

        <div class="donate-thankyou">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.9)"/>
          </svg>
          Thank you — your support means the world to us.
        </div>

        <p>To date, your donations have helped fund:</p>

        <div class="donate-funded">
          <div class="donate-funded-item">Purchase of the budgie-remix.org URL for one year (2016)</div>
          <div class="donate-funded-item">Purchase of the ubuntubudgie.org URL for four years (2016–2020)</div>
          <div class="donate-funded-item">budgie-remix.org three year extension (2017–2020)</div>
          <div class="donate-funded-item">Transfer of budgie-remix.org from WordPress to GoDaddy (2017–2020) — fully funded</div>
          <div class="donate-funded-item">Server fees for ubuntubudgie.org 2017 &amp; 2018 — fully funded by our sponsor <strong>DigitalOcean</strong></div>
        </div>

        <p>Server fees for ubuntubudgie.org 2019 — pending sponsorship</p>

        <p><strong>Long-term Goal — LTS Status.</strong> From 18.04, Long-Term Support is an option Ubuntu Budgie would love to provide to all users. To do this we need a financially sound 3-year model for each LTS release.</p>

        <div class="donate-funded">
          <div class="donate-lts-item">
            <span class="lts-badge lts-funded">Funded</span>
            Expected costs for 2018–2020 (18.04 LTS)
          </div>
          <div class="donate-lts-item">
            <span class="lts-badge lts-funded">Funded</span>
            Expected costs for 2021–2022 (20.04 LTS)
          </div>
          <div class="donate-lts-item">
            <span class="lts-badge lts-unfunded">Not funded</span>
            Expected costs for 2023 (22.04 LTS)
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>Ubuntu Budgie puts you — our community — front and center in everything we do. You can also support Ubuntu Budgie by buying merchandise from our official store on Zazzle: <a href="#">Ubuntu Budgie Store</a></p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>
</BaseLayout>